Recommends: gnome-settings-daemon
Suggests:
 bumblebee,
 nvidia-settings,
 primus,
 xserver-xorg-input-joystick
Provides: steam-login
Replaces: steam-login
Description: launch Steam Big Picture from your login screen
 With the release of Steam Beta, and steam BigPicture mode on Linux, this
 package will put Steam as a login option, so you will be able to open only
 Steam and needed software to make it run correctly.
 It's almost a Steam Desktop.
